FX64 F20 x86_64 Linux

fx64,fx64 linux,linux,google chrome,flash,skype,office,audio,video

FX64 Linux is a Fedora 20 based distro. Google Chrome, Java IcedTea, Adobe Flash Player, Skype & RAR preinstalled. Hand picked essential system, office, multimedia and internet applications. Updates directly from the official Fedora, RPM Fusion and Adobe repositories. Thousands of free applications for every need directly from the open source community. Clean, lean and feature rich FREE AS IN BEER experience!
